<big><small><div align="left"><B><u>Habitat for Humanity Fund Drive Begins</u></B>
<BR>
Tax-deductible donations to the HBA's annual Habitat for Humanity Fund Drive will be accepted 
through January 31, 2002. It takes $50,000 to build a home for a low income family. The HBA's 
fund is currently $11,000. Send checks, payable to the Houston Bar Association, to Campaign for the Homeless, Houston Bar Association, 1001 Fannin, Suite 1300, Houston, Texas 77002.
<BR>
For more information contact <A HREF="mailto:rustyb@hba.org">Rusty Bienvenue</A>.
<P>
<big><small><div align="left"><B><u>Harvest Party Record</u></B>
<BR>This year's Harvest Party raised a record $269,350 in underwriting for the Houston Bar Foundation. 
<A HREF="http://www.hba.org/underwriters.htm">Click here</A> for a complete list of the 52nd Annual Harvest Party Underwriters.<P>
